                        <desc>
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2465">Julian</persName>, 
                            lacking needed clergy, sought the ordination of priests and deacons by
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2751">Sergius</persName> and
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2407">Marion</persName>.
                            <listRelation>
